title: 后台疯狂刷屏！！！
author: Dirito
txt_content: [Server] pool-16-thread-1/WARN Try to asynchronously call InventoryOpenEvent, caught!

replies.author: skyliye
replies.txt_content:
是catserver自带的提示，无影响，我这也有
目前的办法是直接用consolespamfix插件屏蔽掉
复制这个报错到名单里然后/csf reload即可
https://media.forgecdn.net/files ... leSpamFix-1.7.2.jar
